00:00:00,692 --> 00:00:07,814
“Glacier’s Lament” is music and dance choreographed from the data from glaciers melting in the past 60 years. 

2
00:00:07,814 --> 00:00:14,164
“Disappearing Blue” is a self-destructive installation with blue colors sampled from Alaskan glaciers. 

3
00:00:14,164 --> 00:00:19,731
When one glacier calving happens in the world, one vial with color will fall down. 

4
00:00:19,731 --> 00:00:25,024
At the end of the exhibition, all 60 tubes fell down, forming a painting on the canvas beneath. 

